
1) Audience
	Data Analyst
	Data engineer
	Data scientist

2) Subject:
	Action/Info/Required/
	Subject line should be one line summary

3) Organizing information:
	Screenshots:
		picture is worth a thousand words 
		picture is unstructured data, hard to copy paste values

	Unstructured data:
		paragraphs of written explaination
		try to use points and make it structured

	Turning Unstructured to structured data:
		using a table
		topic|values|description
		
	Use points:
		it organizes the email
		split the email into sections
		mention the # of points in the email
		Use # for main a) alpha for upto 5 points
		have seperate email for each resonable topic


4) Formatting & Color:
	Formatting:
		Underline
		Italic
		Bold

	Colors:
		use matching colors for multiple topics in a email
		Font color
		Background color


5) Supporting data:
	data examples
	SQL if possible


6) External reference data/information:
	Using links for details:
		It is challenging to put all the detials in the email
		share links to detail content

	Attachments:
		attachments are a friction point
		try to have small attachments
		have a data table in the email with details in attachements
		make a thumbnail of the main slides (it helps with the curiosity of the reciever)
